<body>
<div><head>禮統</head>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1116_CHANT_001-1a.1"><pb xml:id="CH2e1116_CHANT_001-1a" ed="CHANT" n="001-1a"/><lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1116_CHANT_001-1a.2">天地者，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1116_CHANT_001-1a.3">元氣之所生，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1116_CHANT_001-1a.4">萬物之祖也。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1116_CHANT_001-1a.5">天之為言鎮也，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1116_CHANT_001-1a.6">神也，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1116_CHANT_001-1a.7">珍也。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1116_CHANT_001-1a.8">施生為本，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1116_CHANT_001-1a.9">運轉精神，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1116_CHANT_001-1a.10">功效列陳，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1116_CHANT_001-1a.11">其道可珍重也。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1116_CHANT_001-1a.12">《太平御覽》卷一。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1116_CHANT_001-1a.13">歐陽詢《藝文類聚》卷一。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1116_CHANT_001-1a.14">《後漢書》班固列傳章懷太子《注》。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1116_CHANT_001-1a.15">陸德明《莊子釋文》卷中並引首二句。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1116_CHANT_001-1a.16">瞿曇悉達《開元占經》卷三引首四句作「天之為言顛也，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1116_CHANT_001-1a.17">神水珍也。」<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1116_CHANT_001-2a.1"><pb xml:id="CH2e1116_CHANT_001-2a" ed="CHANT" n="001-2a"/><lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1116_CHANT_001-2a.2">地，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1116_CHANT_001-2a.3">施也，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1116_CHANT_001-2a.4">諦也，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1116_CHANT_001-2a.5">應變施化，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1116_CHANT_001-2a.6">審諦不誤也。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1116_CHANT_001-2a.7">《爾雅‧釋地》邢昺《疏》。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1116_CHANT_001-2a.8">日者，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1116_CHANT_001-2a.9">實也。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1116_CHANT_001-2a.10">形體光實，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1116_CHANT_001-2a.11">人君之象。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1116_CHANT_001-2a.12">《太平御覽》卷三。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1116_CHANT_001-3a.1"><pb xml:id="CH2e1116_CHANT_001-3a" ed="CHANT" n="001-3a"/><lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1116_CHANT_001-3a.2">雲者，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1116_CHANT_001-3a.3">運也，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1116_CHANT_001-3a.4">氣布恩溥博。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1116_CHANT_001-3a.5">《御覽》有「博」字。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1116_CHANT_001-3a.6">也。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1116_CHANT_001-3a.7">《藝文類聚》卷一、《太平御覽》卷八。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1116_CHANT_001-3a.8">雨者，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1116_CHANT_001-3a.9">輔時生養均遍，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1116_CHANT_001-3a.10">故謂之雨。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1116_CHANT_001-3a.11">《太平御覽》卷十。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1116_CHANT_001-4a.1"><pb xml:id="CH2e1116_CHANT_001-4a" ed="CHANT" n="001-4a"/><lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1116_CHANT_001-4a.2">雨凝曰雹。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1116_CHANT_001-4a.3">虞世南《北堂書鈔》卷一百五十二。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1116_CHANT_001-4a.4">所以制辟雍何？<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1116_CHANT_001-4a.5">教化天下也。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1116_CHANT_001-4a.6">辟雍之制奈何？<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1116_CHANT_001-4a.7">《王制》曰：<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1116_CHANT_001-4a.8">辟雍，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1116_CHANT_001-4a.9">圓如璧，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1116_CHANT_001-4a.10">雍以水，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1116_CHANT_001-4a.11">內如覆，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1116_CHANT_001-4a.12">外如偃盤也。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1116_CHANT_001-4a.13">諸侯泮宮，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1116_CHANT_001-4a.14">半有水，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1116_CHANT_001-4a.15">半有宮也。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1116_CHANT_001-4a.16">諸侯所化者少，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1116_CHANT_001-4a.17">故半有宮焉。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1116_CHANT_001-4a.18">三王之制奈何？<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1116_CHANT_001-4a.19">夏天子曰重室，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1116_CHANT_001-4a.20">諸侯曰廣宗；<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1116_CHANT_001-4a.21">殷天子曰廟，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1116_CHANT_001-4a.22">諸侯曰世室；<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1116_CHANT_001-4a.23">周天子曰辟雍，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1116_CHANT_001-4a.24">諸侯曰泮宮，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1116_CHANT_001-4a.25">卿曰庠，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1116_CHANT_001-4a.26">里曰序，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1116_CHANT_001-4a.27">是其制也。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1116_CHANT_001-4a.28">《太平御覽》卷五百三十四。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1116_CHANT_001-4a.29">《史記‧封禪書》司馬貞《索隱》引「諸侯曰泮宮，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1116_CHANT_001-4a.30">半有水，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1116_CHANT_001-4a.31">而半有宮。」<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1116_CHANT_001-4a.32">《白孔六帖》卷三十七引首二句。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1116_CHANT_001-5a.1"><pb xml:id="CH2e1116_CHANT_001-5a" ed="CHANT" n="001-5a"/><lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1116_CHANT_001-5a.2">所以制靈臺何？<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1116_CHANT_001-5a.3">以尊天重民，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1116_CHANT_001-5a.4">備災禦害，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1116_CHANT_001-5a.5">豫防未然也。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1116_CHANT_001-5a.6">夫王者當承順天地，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1116_CHANT_001-5a.7">節禦陰陽也。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1116_CHANT_001-5a.8">夏所以為清臺何？<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1116_CHANT_001-5a.9">明明相承，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1116_CHANT_001-5a.10">太平相續，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1116_CHANT_001-5a.11">故為清臺。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1116_CHANT_001-5a.12">殷為神臺，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1116_CHANT_001-5a.13">周為靈臺何？<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1116_CHANT_001-5a.14">質者據天而王，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1116_CHANT_001-5a.15">天者稱神。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1116_CHANT_001-5a.16">文者據地而王，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1116_CHANT_001-5a.17">地者稱靈，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1116_CHANT_001-5a.18">是其異也。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1116_CHANT_001-5a.19">《太平御覽》卷五百三十四。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1116_CHANT_001-6a.1"><pb xml:id="CH2e1116_CHANT_001-6a" ed="CHANT" n="001-6a"/><lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1116_CHANT_001-6a.2">祭有昭穆，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1116_CHANT_001-6a.3">所以別父子、遠近、長幼、親疏之序而無亂也。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1116_CHANT_001-6a.4">章如愚《山堂考索前集》卷二十九。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1116_CHANT_001-6a.5">天子、諸侯皆為貴，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1116_CHANT_001-6a.6">臣妾服三月，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1116_CHANT_001-6a.7">適夫人為八妾服三月，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1116_CHANT_001-6a.8">八妾為夫人服與舅姑同。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1116_CHANT_001-6a.9">《太平御覽》卷五百四十七。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1116_CHANT_001-7a.1"><pb xml:id="CH2e1116_CHANT_001-7a" ed="CHANT" n="001-7a"/><lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1116_CHANT_001-7a.2">弔生曰唁，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1116_CHANT_001-7a.3">弔死曰弔，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1116_CHANT_001-7a.4">生謂之唁何？<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1116_CHANT_001-7a.5">非為喪之位哭泣之事，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1116_CHANT_001-7a.6">但嗟嘆以言，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1116_CHANT_001-7a.7">故謂之唁。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1116_CHANT_001-7a.8">弔死謂之弔何？<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1116_CHANT_001-7a.9">素有恩，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1116_CHANT_001-7a.10">禮無服屬，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1116_CHANT_001-7a.11">但致哀傷，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1116_CHANT_001-7a.12">故謂之弔。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1116_CHANT_001-7a.13">《北堂書鈔》卷八十五。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1116_CHANT_001-8a.1"><pb xml:id="CH2e1116_CHANT_001-8a" ed="CHANT" n="001-8a"/><lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1116_CHANT_001-8a.2">屍之言矢也，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1116_CHANT_001-8a.3">陳也。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1116_CHANT_001-8a.4">《太平御覽》卷五百四十九。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1116_CHANT_001-8a.5">柩之言久也，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1116_CHANT_001-8a.6">具書其諡，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1116_CHANT_001-8a.7">置棺旁，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1116_CHANT_001-8a.8">萬世久藏也。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1116_CHANT_001-8a.9">《太平御覽》卷五百五十。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1116_CHANT_001-9a.1"><pb xml:id="CH2e1116_CHANT_001-9a" ed="CHANT" n="001-9a"/><lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1116_CHANT_001-9a.2">劓刑法木勝土，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1116_CHANT_001-9a.3">決其皮革也。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1116_CHANT_001-9a.4">《太平御覽》卷六百四十八。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1116_CHANT_001-9a.5">臏刑法金勝木，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1116_CHANT_001-9a.6">去其節目也。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1116_CHANT_001-9a.7">同上。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1116_CHANT_001-9a.8">《北堂書鈔》卷四十四引「臏去節目」。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1116_CHANT_001-10a.1"><pb xml:id="CH2e1116_CHANT_001-10a" ed="CHANT" n="001-10a"/><lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1116_CHANT_001-10a.2">神龜之象，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1116_CHANT_001-10a.3">上員法天，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1116_CHANT_001-10a.4">下方法地，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1116_CHANT_001-10a.5">背上有盤法邱山。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1116_CHANT_001-10a.6">元文交錯，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1116_CHANT_001-10a.7">以成列宿，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1116_CHANT_001-10a.8">五色昭若元錦文，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1116_CHANT_001-10a.9">運轉應四時。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1116_CHANT_001-10a.10">長尺二寸，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1116_CHANT_001-10a.11">明吉凶，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1116_CHANT_001-10a.12">不言而信。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1116_CHANT_001-10a.13">徐堅《初學記》卷三十。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1116_CHANT_001-10a.14">《太平御覽》卷九百三十一。<lb/></seg>
</p>
</div>
